    "body": "The above model was agreed upon by the EIPIP group in Q4 2020 and shared in the [ACD meeting 100](https://youtu.be/5-614J9qNvY?t=3778). \r\n\r\nBerlin is the first upgrade where we're following the process. After giving some more thoughts, I'd like to propose further edits to EIP statuses as below:  \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/29681685/110026914-5042ec80-7cff-11eb-891d-3fe61ae2482d.png)\r\n\r\nI want to propose this because\r\n- A proposal is supposed to be in the _Last call_  for 14 days.\r\n- After _Final_, there can't be any spec change so let's wait till it is deployed on the mainnet. (I was convinced by Micah) \r\n\r\n",
